She was supposed to have money for the services she asked for. I've had my wages docked for this exact circumstance numerous times, and that hairdresser would have, as well. I am not going to go off of one woman's rant as fact, and just because she says the woman was rude, doesn't mean it really went down that way. I've seen way too many customers make up issues and throw tantrums for free services. I'm not saying it didn't happen, either, I'm saying none of us really know and this lady could be an entitled brat, or a repeat offender, or lying. As far as the collateral, she ABSOLUTELY could have come back and accused them of stealing something that wasn't there (I've seen that happen, too).
